snippet.title: A Waddleful Life Pre-Alpha Teaser
snippet.description:
A Waddleful Life is a sweet little game where you play as a duck raising ducklings. Explore a small park while guiding and helping your ducklings grow from tiny hatchlings to their first flight.

Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3238520/A_Waddleful_Life

Follow for updates!
 X: https://x.com/AWaddlefulLife
 Bluesky:  https://bsky.app/profile/awaddlefullife.bsky.social
